                <p class="pb-6">What is data reporting also involves the underlying principles that reporting relies on. It is not a report of numbers, but it must contain clear guidelines to render the information accurate, useful, and actionable in an effective report. In line with these principles, corporations have developed organised data reporting applications to facilitate decision-making and reporting. The following main principles will be used to guarantee effective reporting:</p>

